{"tha-ap306:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap306:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap306:0.3":"Dhammasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap306:1.1":"“Vipassino bhagavato, ","tha-ap306:1.2":"Mahabodhimaho ahu; ","tha-ap306:1.3":"Rukkhatthasseva sambuddho, ","tha-ap306:1.4":"Lokajettho narasabho. ","tha-ap306:2.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap306:2.2":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato; ","tha-ap306:2.3":"Catusaccam pakaseti, ","tha-ap306:2.4":"vacasabhimudirayam. ","tha-ap306:3.1":"Sankhittena ca desento, ","tha-ap306:3.2":"vittharena ca desayam; ","tha-ap306:3.3":"Vivattacchado sambuddho, ","tha-ap306:3.4":"nibbapesi mahajanam. ","tha-ap306:4.1":"Tassaham dhammam sutvana, ","tha-ap306:4.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap306:4.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap306:4.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap306:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap306:5.2":"yam dhammamasunim tada; ","tha-ap306:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap306:5.4":"dhammasavassidam phalam. ","tha-ap306:6.1":"Tettimsamhi ito kappe, ","tha-ap306:6.2":"eko asim mahipati; ","tha-ap306:6.3":"Sutava nama namena, ","tha-ap306:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap306:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap306:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap306:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap306:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhammasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap306:9.1":"Dhammasannakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}